\[z^4 = \operatorname{cis} 60^\circ.\]The solutions to this equation are $\operatorname{cis} 15^\circ,$ $\operatorname{cis} 105^\circ,$ $\operatorname{cis} 195^\circ,$ and $\operatorname{cis} 285^\circ.$

